No, I need to be saved.
No, I want to be saved.

1042
01:19:55,323 --> 01:19:58,087
Please, no. No! Leave me alone!

1043
01:19:58,159 --> 01:20:00,559
You don't want me forgiven!
You want me damned!

1044
