The doctor gave her a sedation to sleep.
She's been working much too hard.

1052
01:20:56,250 --> 01:20:58,081
Yes, of course, indeed.

1053
01:20:58,152 --> 01:21:00,484
Sensitive type, the overstrung type.

1054
01:21:00,621 --> 01:21:03,419
People of her type throw themselves
into everything.

1055
01:21:03,491 --> 01:21:05,015
And then that man...

1056
01:21:05,192 --> 01:21:07,626
<i>...dying in the trench outside...</i>

1057
01:21:08,696 --> 01:21:10,857
What has that got to do with it?

1058
01:21:10,931 --> 01:21:15,391
To people of that type,
any shock is highly injurious.

1059
01:21:16,537 --> 01:21:19,097
Do you remember her first reaction to me?

1060
01:21:22,843 --> 01:21:24,743
Adelle?
I--I have to
go to the doctor.

1061
01:21:24,812 --> 01:21:26,803
I have to go, let me go!

1062
01:21:27,948 --> 01:21:29,438
[Starr]:
It's only I, Mrs. Martin.

1063
01:21:29,750 --> 01:21:32,218
<i>But if I can be of any help,
in any way at all...</i>

1064
