Remember the way she behaved
at the recital?

1068
01:21:44,131 --> 01:21:48,363
- Very nervous for a long time.
- I'm afraid there is something odd...
[Muttering]

1069
01:21:56,110 --> 01:21:58,635
- You've got to get back into bed.
- I--I know.
[Moaning]

1070
01:22:01,749 --> 01:22:04,377
- You must get some sleep.
- I can't sleep.

1071
01:22:04,585 --> 01:22:06,780
Here, take your pill.

1072
01:22:07,221 --> 01:22:08,654
I can't sleep.

1073
01:22:08,956 --> 01:22:10,253
Have you prayed?

1074
01:22:10,558 --> 01:22:12,458
The damned don't pray.

1075
01:22:12,626 --> 01:22:14,787
If you had let me atone, I'd be all right.

1076
01:22:14,862 --> 01:22:18,298
The Lord welcomes sinners
with open arms, but you hit me.

1077
01:22:20,668 --> 01:22:23,193
Linc and I are going out for a while.

1078
01:22:23,304 --> 01:22:24,965
You try and sleep.

1079
01:22:28,209 --> 01:22:30,473
I know why you did it, of course.

1080
01:22:30,544 --> 01:22:32,944
Just like I know
why you're keeping me here.

1081
01:22:33,314 --> 01:22:34,872
You're afraid.
Adelle.

1082
