...you will be damned, too.

1085
01:22:46,594 --> 01:22:50,462
All I want you to do is to get well,
as soon as possible.

1086
01:22:52,233 --> 01:22:55,930
And then I want you to go away,
as far as possible.

1087
01:23:02,624 --> 01:23:03,707
[Door Closing]

1088
