01:24:30,464 --> 01:24:33,605
You're so beautiful. So white, so pure.

1094
01:24:33,615 --> 01:24:34,615
Oh.

1095
01:24:35,417 --> 01:24:36,550
[Whimpering]

1096
01:24:36,618 --> 01:24:37,651
Helen.

1097
01:24:37,719 --> 01:24:38,786
Ah!

1098
01:24:38,854 --> 01:24:40,220
Oh!

1099
01:24:40,941 --> 01:24:42,431
It is only I.

1100
01:24:43,444 --> 01:24:46,038
I'm so sorry.
I always seem to frighten you, don't I?

1101
01:24:50,251 --> 01:24:54,745
I saw this on my way home in a garden
as I passed, and so I borrowed it...

1102
01:24:55,522 --> 01:24:56,887
...for you.

1103
01:25:00,661 --> 01:25:02,026
Ah!
Oh, the thorn.

1104
01:25:02,930 --> 01:25:05,296
Always a thorn somewhere, isn't there?

1105
01:25:05,297 --> 01:25:06,297
[Dog Barking]

1106
01:25:09,534 --> 01:25:10,634
[Chuckles]

1107
01:25:12,606 --> 01:25:14,073
Now, there.

1108
01:25:21,713 --> 01:25:23,043
[Whimpering]

1109
01:25:23,984 --> 01:25:25,508
Now, you're so cold.

1110
01:25:26,253 --> 01:25:29,051
Would you like to go inside for a little?

1111
01:25:29,990 --> 01:25:33,084
