01:26:41,028 --> 01:26:43,929
- I had no intention...
- Honey, wait a minute.

1122
01:26:46,133 --> 01:26:49,330
You know,
you don't have to try and fool me anymore.

1123
01:26:49,703 --> 01:26:52,103
- Well, l...
- You want to marry me?

1124
01:26:52,439 --> 01:26:56,773
I'll tell you something,
I'm crazy about you, I want to marry you.

1125
01:27:00,812 --> 01:27:02,490
[Ball Falling
