01:29:24,606 --> 01:29:25,873
[Dog Barking]

1145
01:29:30,211 --> 01:29:31,411
Oh.

1146
01:30:19,493 --> 01:30:20,694
[Gasping]

1147
01:30:28,502 --> 01:30:29,702
Oh.

1148
01:30:33,975 --> 01:30:35,200
[Screaming]

1149
01:30:36,377 --> 01:30:37,603
Helen.

1150
01:30:42,249 --> 01:30:43,503
No, Adelle,

1151
01:30:44,171 --> 01:30:47,072
I couldn't leave
my poor little creatures, could I?

1152
01:30:47,874 --> 01:30:50,138
I mean, I love them.

1153
01:30:54,548 --> 01:30:58,848
The vet wouldn't take them back,
and no one else would.

1154
01:31:02,356 --> 01:31:04,153
You know, that's exactly...

1155
01:31:05,092 --> 01:31:06,957
...what happened with...

1156
01:31:08,328 --> 01:31:10,353
...Lenny's father, I...

1157
01:31:11,999 --> 01:31:14,194
I had to leave him, too.

1158
01:31:14,501 --> 01:31:16,162
After a while...

1159
01:31:16,703 --> 01:31:19,900
...I couldn't stand him,
I couldn't stand him to touch me.

1160
01:31:22,376 --> 01:31:24,241
If you love them...

1161
01:31:25,278 --> 01:31:26,939
...you can't just leave them.

1162
01:31:30,450 --> 01:31:32,111
You have to...

1163
