If you're trying to tell me
that you killed your husband...

1165
01:31:42,929 --> 01:31:44,920
...I just don't believe you.

1166
01:31:46,466 --> 01:31:48,229
I don't believe you.

1167
01:31:49,269 --> 01:31:50,759
Well, I did.

1168
01:31:51,605 --> 01:31:53,004
It's the truth.

1169
01:31:56,209 --> 01:31:57,801
I pushed him.

1170
01:31:58,478 --> 01:32:00,708
<i>You know, like I pushed that...</i>

1171
01:32:03,383 --> 01:32:04,975
<i>I always...</i>

1172
01:32:05,919 --> 01:32:09,377
I always told you that I was the guilty one,
remember?

1173
01:32:11,958 --> 01:32:14,085
You wouldn't let me speak, Adelle.

1174
01:32:14,194 --> 01:32:16,128
You wouldn't help me.

1175
01:32:16,296 --> 01:32:19,356
You didn't want to hear the truth.

1176
01:32:23,070 --> 01:32:26,267
I think you should speak now. You must.

1177
01:32:29,443 --> 01:32:32,469
I'm going to call Sister Alma...

1178
01:32:32,879 --> 01:32:35,313
...and then I'm going to tell her...

1179
01:32:35,382 --> 01:32:38,613
...to talk to you and to listen to you...

1180
01:32:38,785 --> 01:32:43,017
...and to let you know
that God has forgiven you.

1181
01:32:43,990 --> 01:32:46,117
- You'd do that?
- Yes.

1182
01:32:46,193 --> 01:32:47,820
You'd really do that?

1183
01:32:47,894 --> 01:32:50,260
Thank you, Adelle. Thank you.

1184
01:32:51,231 --> 01:32:53,791
I want to do everything...

1185
01:32:54,067 --> 01:32:57,230
...that you think best. I really do.

1186
01:33:02,342 --> 01:33:05,573
You see, everything will be all right.

1187
01:33:07,147 --> 01:33:10,139
Sister Alma will understand and help you.

1188
01:33:10,550 --> 01:33:13,383
And this time I'll let her.

1189
01:33:14,087 --> 01:33:16,920
Thank you, Adelle,
you're so good to me.
[Laughing]

1190
01:33:17,591 --> 01:33:20,185
